INSERT INTO `skills` VALUES (2,'Love and Peace',1,'Lvl: 1 - This skill deals 100% damage to a large radius of enemies and renders melee enemies unable to use physical attacks for a short period of time.','Lvl: 61 - This skill deals 150% damage to a large radius of enemies and renders melee enemies unable to use physical attacks for a short period of time.\nLvl: 121 - This skill deals 150% damage to a large radius of enemies and renders all enemies unable to attack for a short period of time. ','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Angelo'),(12,'Encourage',2,'Lvl: 11 - Angelo plays a war song that allows his most injured ally to recover 90% of Angelo\'s attack rating in the form of health.','Lvl: 21 - Angelo plays a war song that allows his most injured ally to recover 110% of Angelo\'s attack rating in the form of health. \nLvl: 81 - Angelo plays a war song that allows the weakest ally and the ally with the highest Attack Rating to recover 110% of Angelo\'s Attack Rating in the form of health while simultaneously increasing their attack speed. \nLvl: 141 - Angelo plays a war song that allows the weakest ally and the ally with the highest Attack Rating to recover 130%of Angelo\'s Attack Rating in the form of health while simultaneously increasing their attack speed.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Angelo'),(22,'Restoration',3,'Lvl: 41 - Angelo\'s tune releases a musical note that hits 2 different heroes. If the note hits an enemy they will receive damage but if it hits an ally they will be healed for a certain amount.','Lvl: 101 - Angelo\'s tune releases a musical note that hits 3 different heroes. If the note hits an enemy they will receive damage but if it hits an ally they will be healed for a certain amount.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Angelo'),(32,'Venomous Bile',1,'Lvl: 1 - Ankhira spits lethal venom at the enemy with the most health dealing 100% damage to them and subsequently causes 60% damage per second over a duration of 8 seconds.','Lvl: 61 - Ankhira spits lethal venom at the enemy with the most health dealing 100% damage to them and subsequently slowing their movement speed and causing 60% damage per second over a duration of 8 seconds \nLvl: 121 - Ankhira spits lethal venom at the enemy with the most health dealing 100% damage to them and subsequently slowing their movement speed and causing 60% damage per second over a duration of 20 seconds','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ankhira'),(42,'Corrosion',2,'Lvl: 11 - Ankhira spits corrosive venom onto her target\'s armor dealing 120% damage to them. The corrosive venom also reduces the target\'s armor rating by 35%.','Lvl: 21 - Ankhira spits corrosive venom onto her target\'s armor dealing 140% damage to them. The corrosive venom also reduces the target\'s armor rating by 35%. \nLvl: 81 - Ankhira spits corrosive venom onto her target\'s armor dealing 140% damage to them. The corrosive venom also reduces the target\'s armor rating by 35% and causes the target to gradually lose energy as a result of shock. \nLvl: 141 - Ankhira spits corrosive venom onto her target\'s armor dealing 160% damage to them. The corrosive venom also reduces the target\'s armor rating by 35% and causes the target to gradually lose energy as a result of shock.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ankhira'),(52,'Coccoon',3,'Lvl: 41 - Ankhira shoots a web at an enemy cocooning and thus immobilizing them for up to 6 seconds. When the affected target loses 25% of their maximum health during the cocoon phase the effect will be broken in advance.','Lvl: 101 - Ankhira shoots a web at an enemy cocooning and thus immobilizing them and making them lose energy in the struggle for up to 6 seconds. When the affected target loses 25% of their maximum health during the cocoon phase the effect will be broken in advance.Enemies lose 2% energy points per second while cocooned.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ankhira'),(62,'Force of Nature',1,'Lvl: 1 - Arden calls forth the full force of mother nature to hit all enemies successively. Each hit deals 150% magic damage. Maximum amount of hits limited to 5 per time.','Lvl: 61 - Arden calls forth the full force of mother nature to hit all enemies successively. Each hit deals 150% magic damage. The targeted enemy can be hit multiple times. Maximum amount of hits limited to 5 per time.\nLvl: 121 - Arden calls forth the full force of mother nature to hit all enemies successively. First hit deals #.PlusRatio.Per# magic damage and is increased by 10% per further successive hit (maximum amount of hits limited to 5 per time)','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Arden'),(72,'Entangling Roots',2,'Lvl: 11 - Arden raises tree roots from the ground that entrap 1 enemy targets, dealing 70% damage to them. The entangling roots cause damage over time and prevent enemies from moving, dodging or attacking while entangled.','Lvl: 21 - Arden raises tree roots from the ground that entrap 1 enemy targets, dealing 80% damage to them. The entangling roots cause damage over time and prevent enemies from moving, dodging or attacking while entangled. \nLvl: 81 - Arden raises tree roots from the ground that entrap 2 enemy targets, dealing 80% damage to them. The entangling roots cause damage over time and prevent enemies from moving, dodging or attacking while entangled. \nLvl: 141 - Arden raises tree roots from the ground that entrap 3 enemy targets, dealing 80% damage to them. The entangling roots cause damage over time and prevent enemies from moving, dodging or attacking while entangled.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Arden'),(82,'Shield of Thorns',3,'Lvl: 41 - Arden creates a protective shield made of thorns around an ally that is able to deflect 80% magic damage back at the aggressing enemy. Deflected damage is based upon Arden\'s Attack Rating. This ability can be activated every 0.13 seconds.','Lvl: 101 - Arden creates a protective shield made of thorns around an ally that is able to deflect 80% magic damage back at the aggressing enemy, slowing them. Deflected damage is based upon Arden\'s Attack Rating. This ability can be activated every 0.13 seconds.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Arden'),(92,'Divine Fury',1,'Lvl: 1 - Athalia attacks her enemies with lightning speed and precision, slashing them three times from various positions on the battlefield. Each slash deals 160% damage to all enemies in her path. The third slash has a 100% critical strike chance.','Lvl: 81 - Enemies that are struck more than once are dealt an additional 50% damage. \nLvl: 161 - Damage increased by up to 190%','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Athalia'),(102,'Judgement',2,'Lvl: 11 - Athalia descends from the heavens onto the battlefield and targets the enemy directly opposite her, inflicting 280% damage on them. Once the initial attack has finished, Athalia will stand and attack the targeted enemy normally. Enemies will not be able to regenerate energy when attacked by this ability.','Lvl: 21 - Damage increased by up to 290% \nLvl: 101 - Targeted enemy cannot regenerate energy from attacks for 5 seconds after initial attack \nLvl: 181 - Damage increased by up to 310%','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Athalia'),(112,'Purging Frenzy',3,'Lvl: 41 - Athalia unleashes a multi-staged attack on the enemy nearest to her, with the final blow dealing 150% damage to the target that also leaves them stunned for 2 seconds.','Lvl: 121 - Stun effect lasts for up to 3 seconds \nLvl: 201 - Final attack damage increased to 170% damage.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Athalia'),(122,'Protection',4,'Lvl: 61 - Athalia uses a divine aura that allows herself to mitigate 8% of all received damage for every ally still alive on the battlefield.','Lvl: 141 - Each living ally raises Athalia\'s damage by 3% \nLvl: 221 - Each living ally raises Athalia\'s damage by 4%','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Athalia'),(132,'Divine Light',1,'Lvl: 1 - Belinda uses her divine power to attack a large area of enemies 4 times. Each successful hit deals 110% magic damage to the enemy targets.','Lvl: 81 - Belinda unleashes an attack that hits multiple enemies 4 times. The first hit deals 110% magic damage and then increases per each successive hit. \nLvl: 161 - Belinda unleashes an attack that hits multiple enemies 5 times. The first hit deals 110% magic damage and then increases per each successive hit.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Belinda'),(142,'Divine Retribution',2,'Lvl: 11 - Belinda fires an orb of divine energy towards her enemies. The ball explodes on impact with the first enemy it reaches. Surrounding enemies consequently suffer 160% damage.','Lvl: 21 - Belinda fires an orb of divine energy towards her enemies. The ball explodes on impact with the first enemy it reaches. Surrounding enemies consequently suffer 180% damage. \nLvl: 101 - Belinda fires an orb of divine energy towards her enemies. The ball explodes on impact with the first enemy it reaches. Surrounding enemies consequently suffer 180% damage and have their accuracy reduced for a period of time. \nLvl: 181 - Belinda fires an orb of divine energy towards her enemies. The ball explodes on impact with the first enemy it reaches. Surrounding enemies consequently suffer 210% damage and have their accuracy reduced for a period of time.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Belinda'),(152,'Brilliance',3,'Lvl: 41 - Belinda\'s Crit Rating is increased by 12%.','Lvl: 121 - Belinda\'s crit rating is increased by 12%. When Belinda critically strikes an enemy their magic resistance will be permanently reduced by 5%. This ability can be stacked up to 4 times. \nLvl: 201 - Belinda\'s crit rating is increased by 18%. When Belinda critically strikes an enemy their magic resistance will be permanently reduced by 5%. This ability can be stacked up to 4 times.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Belinda'),(162,'Blessing',4,'Lvl: 61 - Belinda blesses the ally with the highest Attack Rating, raising their Attack Rating by 15% and Crit Rating by 15%.','Lvl: 141 - Belinda blesses two allies with the highest Attack Rating, raising their Attack Rating by 15% and crit rating by 15%. \nLvl: 221 - Belinda blesses two allies with the highest Attack Rating, raising their Attack Rating by 20% and crit rating by 20%.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Belinda'),(172,'Whirlwind',1,'Lvl: 1 - Brutus hacks at his enemies twice before spinning into a frenzy, dealing damage to them. Brutus is impervious to any mind control abilities while spinning.','Lvl: 81 - Brutus hacks at his enemies twice before spinning into a frenzy, dealing damage to them. Brutus is impervious to magic damage and any mind control abilities while spinning. \nLvl: 161 - Brutus hacks at his enemies twice before spinning into a frenzy, dealing damage to them and converting 35% of the damage back into health. Brutus is impervious to any controlling abilities while spinning.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Brutus'),(182,'Roar',2,'Lvl: 11 - Brutus lets out a terrifying roar that causes enemies to become more vulnerable. Any physical damage dealt to enemies is increased by 25%.','Lvl: 21 - Brutus lets out a terrifying roar that causes enemies to become more vulnerable. Any physical damage dealt to enemies is increased by 30% \nLvl: 101 - Brutus lets out a terrifying roar that causes enemies to become more vulnerable. Physical damage received by enemies is increased by 40% and cannot be dodged. \nLvl: 181 - Brutus lets out a terrifying roar that causes enemies to become more vulnerable. Physical damage received by enemies is increased by 50% and cannot be dodged.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Brutus'),(192,'Brutal Defiance',3,'Lvl: 41 - Brutus\' damage output is raised according to how low his health falls. Brutus\' Attack Rating can be increased by up to 90%.','Lvl: 121 - When Brutus\' life is dangerously low his damage will be increased by up to 90% and his movement speed will be increased by up to 25%. \nLvl: 201 - When Brutus\' life is dangerously low his damage will be increased by up to 100% and his movement speed will be increased by up to 25%.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Brutus'),(202,'Last Gasp',4,'Lvl: 61 - When Brutus is dealt a fatal blow he is able to retain 1 health point and is immune to all subsequent damage for 4 seconds. Ability can only be used once.','Lvl: 141 - When Brutus is dealt a fatal blow he is able to retain 1 health point and is immune to all subsequent damage for 7 seconds. Ability can only be used once. \nLvl: 221 - When Brutus is dealt a fatal blow he is able to retain 1 health point and is immune to all subsequent damage for 8 seconds. Ability can only be used once.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Brutus'),(212,'Joust',1,'Lvl: 1 - Estrilda uses her lance to send an enemy flying and follows up by landing a flurry of consecutive strikes on them.','Lvl: 81 - Estrilda uses her lance to send an enemy flying and follows up by landing a flurry of consecutive strikes on them. If this attack results in the death of an enemy then Estrilda\'s attack speed and Attack Rating will be increased for a period of time. \nLvl: 161 - Estrilda uses her lance to send an enemy flying and follows up by landing a flurry of consecutive strikes on them. If this attack results in the death of an enemy then all member of Estrilda\'s team including herself will have their attack speed and Attack Rating increased for a period of time.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Estrilda'),(222,'Royal Charge',2,'Lvl: 11 - Estrilda charges into the enemies ranks, dealing 200% damage to anyone in her path. Estrilda is immune to control abilities while charging.','Lvl: 21 - Estrilda charges into the enemies ranks, dealing 230% damage to anyone in her path. Estrilda is immune to control abilities while charging. \nLvl: 101 - Estrilda charges into the enemies ranks, dealing 240% damage to anyone in her path and knocks enemies over. Estrilda is immune to control abilities while charging. \nLvl: 181 - Estrilda charges into the enemies ranks, dealing 250% damage to anyone in her path. While charging damage received reduced by 30% and Estrilda is immune to all enemy control abilities.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Estrilda'),(232,'Inspire',3,'Lvl: 41 - Estrilda increases her allies\' morale by waving her flag. Nearby allies\' attack ratings are temporarily increased.','Lvl: 121 - Estrilda increases her allies\' morale by waving her flag. Nearby allies\' attack ratings are temporarily increased and also restores 100 of their energy points. \nLvl: 201 - Estrilda increases her allies\' morale by waving her flag. Nearby allies\' attack ratings are temporarily increased and also restores150 of their energy points.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Estrilda'),(242,'Ridicule',4,'Lvl: 61 - Estrilda swipes at an enemy with her lance knocking them backwards causing 200% damage. She then proceeds to ridicule the enemy, distracting them and resulting in her teammates receiving less damage from the targeted enemy.','Lvl: 141 - Estrilda swipes at an enemy with her lance knocking them backwards inflicting 200% damage. She then proceeds to ridicule the enemy, distracting them and resulting in her teammates receiving less damage from any enemies that are in close proximity to the affected target. \nLvl: 221 - Estrilda swipes at an enemy with her lance knocking them backwards inflicting 200% damage. She then proceeds to ridicule the enemy, distracting them and resulting in her teammates receiving less damage from any enemies that are in close proximity to the affected target.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Estrilda'),(252,'Fissure',1,'Lvl: 1 - Ezizh causes an explosion that deals 180% damage to any surrounding enemies. The explosion causes part of the ground to burn, damaging any enemies standing upon it for 5 seconds.','Lvl: 81 - Reduces the Attack Ratings of enemies standing on the burning ground by 40% \nLvl: 161 - Damage increased by up to 220%','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ezizh'),(262,'Feeble Mind',2,'Lvl: 11 - Ezizh mind controls the enemy farthest away from himself, preventing them from using any attacks while also forcing them to walk towards him. Once the enemy has reached him, Ezizh deals 210% damage to the mind controlled enemy.','Lvl: 21 - Damage increased by up to 220% \nLvl: 101 - Enemy\'s Attack Rating is reduced by 30% for 5 seconds after being dealt damage \nLvl: 181 - Damage increased by up to 230%','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ezizh'),(272,'Horrify',3,'Lvl: 41 - Ezizh launches an ungodly shockwave towards all of his enemies that inflicts 160% damage upon them, rendering them unable to cast their ultimate abilities for 3 seconds.','Lvl: 121 - Prevents enemies using ultimate abilities for 2 seconds every time one of Ezizh\'s teammates uses an ultimate ability. \nLvl: 201 - Damage increased by up to 180%','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ezizh'),(282,'Mental Fury',4,'Lvl: 61 - Ezizh enrages his teammates, allowing them to to regain 12 energy per second.','Lvl: 141 - Ezizh\'s teammates are able to regain energy after his death, however the effect\'s efficiency is reduced by 50% \nLvl: 221 - Restores 14 Energy per second','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ezizh'),(292,'Purification',1,'Lvl: 1 - Fawkes deals 130% damage to all enemies on the battlefield and removes the majority of buffs they may be using.','Lvl: 81 - Fawkes deals 130% damage to all enemies on the battlefield and removes the majority of buffs they may be using. Removes majority of de-buffs from allied heroes. \nLvl: 161 - Fawkes deals 140% damage to all enemies on the battlefield and removes the majority of buffs they may be using. Removes majority of de-buffs from allied heroes.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Faukes'),(302,'Abate',2,'Lvl: 11 - Fawkes reduces an enemy\'s attack speed by 35% for 6 seconds.','Lvl: 21 - Fawkes reduces an enemy\'s attack speed by 45% for 6 seconds. \nLvl: 101 - Fawkes reduces an enemy\'s attack speed by 35% for 6 seconds. Enemy\'s energy regeneration reduced by 60%. \nLvl: 181 - Fawkes reduces an enemy\'s attack speed by 35% for 6 seconds. Enemy\'s energy regeneration reduced by 60%. Haste is increased for 7.5 seconds','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Faukes'),(312,'Confine',3,'Lvl: 41 - Fawkes deals 50% damage to an enemy and then locks them in his coffin for 7 seconds. The affected enemy cannot attack or be attacked while inside the coffin.','Lvl: 121 - Fawkes deals 50% damage to an enemy and then locks them in his coffin for 8 seconds. The affected enemy cannot attack or be attacked while inside the coffin. \nLvl: 201 - Fawkes deals 50% damage to an enemy and then locks them in his coffin for 9 seconds. The affected enemy cannot attack or be attacked while inside the coffin.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Faukes'),(322,'Silver Bolt',4,'Lvl: 61 - Silver Bolt raises Fawkes\' normal attack damage by 20% and deals a further additional 40% damage to de-buffed enemies.','Lvl: 141 - Silver Bolt raises Fawkes\' normal attack damage by 20% and deals a further additional 40% damage to de-buffed enemies. Restores 40 Energy per hit. \nLvl: 221 - Silver Bolt raises Fawkes\' normal attack damage by 30% and deals a further additional 40% damage to de-buffed enemies. Restores 40 Energy per hit.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Faukes'),(332,'Nether Blaze',1,'Lvl: 1 - Fires a demonic arrow that hits all enemies on the battlefield causing them to suffer 170% damage. All enemies that are hurt by the arrow are haunted by an evil spirit that inflicts an additional 25% on them.','Lvl: 81 - Fires a demonic arrow that hits all enemies on the battlefield causing them to suffer 170% damage. All enemies that are hurt by the arrow are haunted by an evil spirit that inflicts an additional 25% on them. Spirits\' attack speeds are increased for 6 seconds. \nLvl: 161 - Fires a demonic arrow that hits all enemies on the battlefield causing them to suffer 220% damage. All enemies that are hurt by the arrow are haunted by an evil spirit that inflicts an additional 25% on them. Spirits\' attack speeds are increased for 6 seconds.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ferael'),(342,'Accursed Arrow',2,'Lvl: 11 - Fires a cursed arrow at an enemy, dealing 140% damage. The cursed arrow causes an evil spirit to haunt the enemy for 10 seconds. Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities will attack their targets once every 3 seconds','Lvl: 21 - Fires a cursed arrow at an enemy, dealing 170% damage. The cursed arrow causes an evil spirit to haunt the enemy for 10 seconds. Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities will attack their targets once every 3 seconds \nLvl: 101 - Fires a cursed arrow at an enemy, dealing 170% damage. The cursed arrow causes an evil spirit to haunt the enemy for 10 seconds. Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities will attack their targets once every 3 seconds.Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities will deduct 15 of their target\'s energy points per attack \nLvl: 181 - Fires a cursed arrow at an enemy, dealing 170% damage. The cursed arrow causes an evil spirit to haunt the enemy for 10 seconds. Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities will attack their targets once every 3 seconds.Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities will deduct 15 of their target\'s energy points per attack.Any spirits which are summoned due to one of Ferael\'s abilities have a chance to interrupt their enemies\' attacks each time they attack them.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ferael'),(352,'Terrorize',3,'Lvl: 41 - Terrifies and stuns 2 heroes for 10 seconds and summons an evil spirit which haunts them for 2 seconds.','Lvl: 121 - Terrifies and stuns 3 heroes for 10 seconds and summons an evil spirit which haunts them for 2 seconds. \nLvl: 201 - Terrifies and stuns 3 heroes for 10 seconds and summons an evil spirit which haunts them for 3 seconds.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ferael'),(362,'Corrupted Spirit',4,'Lvl: 61 - Summons an evil spirit from any fallen heroes\' corpse that then haunts an enemy for 10 seconds.','Lvl: 141 - Summons an evil spirit from any fallen heroes\' corpse that then haunts an enemy for 10 seconds. All spirits which are summoned by any of Ferael\'s abilities will remain on the battlefield for 3 seconds. \nLvl: 221 - Summons an evil spirit from any fallen heroes\' corpse that then haunts an enemy for 10 seconds. All spirits which are summoned by any of Ferael\'s abilities will remain on the battlefield for 5 seconds.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Ferael'),(372,'Collision',1,'Lvl: 1 - Golus charges down an enemy in front of him inflicting 250% damage on them. Enemy is also stunned.','Lvl: 61 - Golus charges down an enemy in front of him sending them hurtling backwards towards their team, inflicting 250% damage on them and leaving them stunned. Any enemies in the path of attack will suffer damage. \nLvl: 121 - Golus charges down an enemy in front of him sending them hurtling backwards towards their team, inflicting 250% damage on them and leaving them stunned. Any enemies in the path of attack will suffer damage and be left stunned.','2019-05-08 05:03:42','2019-05-08 05:03:42','Golus'),(382,'Outburst',2,'Lvl: 11 - Golus smashes the ground furiously with his hooves causing a shockwave that deals 170% damage to nearby enemies.','Lvl: 21 - Golus smashes the ground furiously with his hooves causing a shockwave that deals 180% damage to nearby enemies. \nLvl: 81 - Golus smashes the ground furiou